INSERT INTO `chat_history` VALUES (1,NULL,'1777573767.464799','kelan ba unang date nag time in and time si jeremy pogi ng am at pm?','Hi, I found Jeremy Pogi\'s first time-in records for you. According to our database, his first AM time-in was at 6:00 AM and his first PM time-in was at 12:00 PM. These are the earliest recorded time-ins for Jeremy. Let me know if you need more information.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:29:29','2026-04-30 18:29:29'),(2,NULL,'1777573905.055776','ano ba nag meron dito sa admin dashboard natin','Kumusta. Sa tingin ko, wala tayong nakitang mga admin users sa dashboard natin. Ang resulta ng query ay wala, kaya\'t hindi natin nakita ang anumang record. Ibig sabihin nito, walang mga account na may role na \'admin\' sa sistema natin. Kung kailangan mo ng tulong sa pag-create ng admin account, pwede kitang tulungan.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:31:46','2026-04-30 18:31:46'),(3,NULL,'1777573917.878061','paano mag logout sa system natin','Upang mag-logout sa system, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n1. **Pumunta sa Welcome Page**: Siguraduhin na nasa welcome page ka ng system.\n2. **Hanapin ang Login/Logout Button**: Sa itaas na parte ng page, sa tabi ng navigation bar, mayroong isang button na may label na \"Login\" o \"Logout\".\n3. **I-click ang Logout Button**: Kung ikaw ay nakalogin, ang button ay may label na \"Logout\". I-click mo ito upang simulan ang proseso ng logout.\n4. **Kumpirma ang Logout**: Matapos mong i-click ang logout button, lilitaw ang isang prompt na hihingi ng kumpirma sa iyong logout. Pindutin ang \"OK\" o \"Confirm\" upang tuluyan mong mai-logout.\n5. **Balik sa Welcome Page**: Matapos mong mai-logout, babalik ka sa welcome page ng system.\n\nAdmin Steps:\nKung ikaw ay isang admin, ang proseso ng logout ay pareho sa mga regular na user. Walang karagdagang hakbang na kinakailangan upang mag-logout bilang isang admin.\n\nImportante:\n- Siguraduhin na ikaw ay nakalogout sa system bago mo iwanan ang computer o device upang maiwasan ang anumang potensyal na seguridad na mga isyu.\n- Kung mayroon kang mga hindi na-save na mga gawain o mga dokumento, siguraduhin na mai-save mo ang lahat bago ka mag-logout upang maiwasan ang anumang pagkawala ng data.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 18:32:00','2026-04-30 18:32:00'),(4,NULL,'1777574092.163992','paano baguhin ang time in and time out ng employee? meron bang mga kailangang documents ?','Kahit na gusto mong baguhin ang time in and time out ng isang empleyado, hindi natin nakita ang anumang record sa ating database. Ibig sabihin nito, wala tayong mga dokumento o record na makikita para sa empleyadong ito. Kung gusto mo talagang magbaguhin ng oras, maaari mong simulan ang proseso ng pagpapakita ng mga kailangang dokumento, pero sa ngayon, wala tayong nakikitang mga detalye. Pakisubukan na makipag-ugnay sa ating HR department para sa karagdagang impormasyon.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:34:54','2026-04-30 18:34:54'),(5,1,'1777574197.276953','Test: How do I register a new employee?','To register a new employee, follow these steps:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Log in to the admin portal**: First, you need to log in to the admin portal using your credentials. You can do this by clicking on the \"Login\" button on the top right corner of the page.\n2. **Navigate to the Personnel section**: After logging in, navigate to the Personnel section. You can do this by clicking on the \"Personnel\" link in the top navigation bar.\n3. **Click on the \"Stats Grid\" card**: On the Personnel page, you will see a \"Stats Grid\" section. Click on the card that displays the total number of personnel.\n4. **Click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" button**: Unfortunately, the provided code does not explicitly show the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" button. However, based on the context, it is likely that you will find this button on the Personnel page or on a related page.\n\n**Employee Registration Wizard:**\n\n1. **Step 1: Personal details**: Fill in the employee\'s personal details, such as name, address, and contact information. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n2. **Step 2: Account details**: Fill in the employee\'s account details, such as username and password. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n3. **Step 3: Employment details**: Fill in the employee\'s employment details, such as job title, department, and employment date. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n4. **Step 4: Contact details**: Fill in the employee\'s contact details, such as phone number and email address. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n5. **Step 5: Gov IDs**: Fill in the employee\'s government-issued IDs, such as ID number and expiration date. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n6. **Step 6: Review and submit**: Review all the details you have entered and submit the registration form.\n\n**Validation rules:**\n\n* Please note that some fields may be required or have specific validation rules, such as password strength or email format. Make sure to fill in all the required fields and follow the validation rules to successfully register a new employee.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to register a new employee. If you encounter any issues or have further questions, please don\'t hesitate to ask.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\"]','2026-04-30 18:36:39','2026-04-30 18:36:39'),(7,NULL,'1777574209.690193','Test: What is my attendance?','Database error: 1242 (21000): Subquery returns more than 1 row','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 18:36:50','2026-04-30 18:36:50'),(8,NULL,'1777574381.423025','how to register new employee?','To register a new employee, follow these steps:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Log in to the admin dashboard**: First, make sure you are logged in to the admin dashboard with the correct credentials.\n2. **Navigate to the personnel page**: Click on the \"Personnel\" tab or menu item to access the personnel management page.\n3. **Click on the \"Add New Employee\" button**: Look for a button that says \"Add New Employee\" or \"Register New Employee\" and click on it.\n4. **Fill in the employee details**: A form will appear where you need to fill in the employee\'s details, such as:\n	* First name\n	* Last name\n	* Email address\n	* Job title\n	* Department\n	* Date of birth\n	* Contact information (phone number, address, etc.)\n5. **Upload required documents**: You may need to upload required documents, such as:\n	* ID proof (passport, driver\'s license, etc.)\n	* Resume or CV\n	* Other relevant documents\n6. **Set up employee credentials**: Create a username and password for the new employee, or generate a default password that the employee can change later.\n7. **Save the employee details**: Once you have filled in all the required fields, click on the \"Save\" or \"Register\" button to create the new employee account.\n8. **Verify employee information**: Review the employee\'s information to ensure everything is accurate and complete.\n\n**Validation rules:**\n\n* Make sure to fill in all required fields, as indicated by asterisks (*) or other visual cues.\n* Ensure that the email address is unique and not already in use by another employee.\n* Verify that the uploaded documents are in the correct format (e.g., PDF, JPEG, etc.) and meet the required specifications.\n\n**What happens next:**\n\n* The new employee will receive an email with their login credentials and a link to reset their password.\n* The employee will be able to log in to the system and access their profile, where they can update their information and change their password.\n* The admin will be able to view the new employee\'s profile and manage their access to different features and modules within the system.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\"]','2026-04-30 18:39:43','2026-04-30 18:39:43'),(9,NULL,'1777574784.911362','Find administrator','I\'ve searched our database for an administrator, but unfortunately, no results were found. It looks like there are no users with the \'admin\' role in our system. If you\'re trying to get in touch with someone for assistance, I\'d be happy to help you explore other options. Please let me know how I can further assist you.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:46:26','2026-04-30 18:46:26'),(10,NULL,'1777575883.778092','How many people work here?','To find out how many people work in your organization, you can follow these steps:\n\n**Step 1: Access the Chatbot**\nGo to the chatbot interface, usually found on the main page or a dedicated chat window. You can also access it through the admin dashboard.\n\n**Step 2: Type Your Question**\nIn the chat window, type your question: \"How many people work here?\" You can also use variations of this question, such as \"What is the total number of employees?\" or \"How many staff members do we have?\"\n\n**Step 3: Send Your Question**\nClick the \"Send\" button or press Enter to submit your question to the chatbot.\n\n**Step 4: View the Response**\nThe chatbot will process your question and provide a response. If your question is valid, the chatbot will display the total number of employees in your organization.\n\n**Step 5: Verify the Information (Optional)**\nIf you want to verify the information, you can access the admin dashboard and navigate to the \"Departments\" or \"Employees\" section. There, you can find the total number of employees listed.\n\n**Admin Steps:**\nIf you are an admin, you can also follow these steps to find the total number of employees:\n\n1. Log in to the admin dashboard.\n2. Navigate to the \"Departments\" or \"Employees\" section.\n3. Look for the \"Total Personnel\" or \"Total Employees\" field, which displays the total number of employees in your organization.\n\nNote: The chatbot uses natural language processing to understand your question, so you can ask your question in a conversational tone. The chatbot will do its best to provide an accurate response based on the data available in the system.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\test-chatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Models\\\\Employee.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:04:45','2026-04-30 19:04:45'),(11,NULL,'1777575928.876985','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, you can follow these steps:\n\n**Step 1: Login to the System**\nFirst, you need to log in to the system. Click on the \"Login\" button on the top right corner of the page and enter your email and password. If you don\'t have an account, you can sign up by clicking on the \"Signup\" button.\n\n**Step 2: Access the Admin Dashboard**\nAfter logging in, you will be redirected to the admin dashboard. If you are an admin user, you will see a dashboard with various options.\n\n**Admin Steps:**\nTo access the employee registration data, follow these steps:\n\n**Step 3: Click on the \"Personnel\" Option**\nOn the admin dashboard, click on the \"Personnel\" option. This will take you to a page where you can manage employee data.\n\n**Step 4: Click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\"**\nOn the personnel page, click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" option. This will take you to a wizard that guides you through the employee registration process.\n\n**Step 5: Complete the Wizard**\nHowever, since you want to know how many employees are registered, you don\'t need to complete the wizard. Instead, look for a button or link that says \"View Registered Employees\" or \"Employee List\".\n\n**Step 6: View the Employee List**\nClick on the \"View Registered Employees\" or \"Employee List\" button. This will take you to a page that displays a list of all registered employees.\n\n**Step 7: Check the Employee Count**\nOn the employee list page, you can see the total number of employees registered in the system. You can also use the search or filter options to narrow down the list and get the count of employees based on specific criteria.\n\nAlternatively, you can also use the chatbot feature to ask the question \"ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?\" (how many employees are registered in the system?). The chatbot will respond with the total number of registered employees.\n\nNote: The exact steps may vary depending on the system\'s configuration and the user\'s role. These steps are based on the provided codebase and may not match the actual system\'s workflow.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:05:31','2026-04-30 19:05:31'),(12,1,'1777576046.725553','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Login to the system**: First, you need to log in to the system using your valid credentials. Click on the \"Login\" button on the top right corner of the page and enter your email and password. If you don\'t have an account, you can sign up by clicking on the \"Signup\" button.\n\n2. **Access the Admin Dashboard**: After logging in, if you are an admin, you will be redirected to the admin dashboard. If you are not an admin, you may not have access to the employee registration data.\n\n3. **Admin steps:** As an admin, you can follow these steps:\n    * Click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" button or navigate to the employee management section.\n    * Look for a button or link that says \"View All Employees\" or \"Employee List\".\n    * Click on this button to view the list of all registered employees.\n\n4. **View Employee List**: Once you are on the employee list page, you can see the total number of employees registered in the system. This information is usually displayed at the top of the page or in a sidebar.\n\n5. **Use the Chatbot (Alternative Method)**: If you are not an admin or do not have access to the admin dashboard, you can use the chatbot feature to find out how many employees are registered in the system.\n    * Click on the chatbot icon or button on the page.\n    * Type a message in the chat window, such as \"ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?\" (how many employees are registered in the system?).\n    * The chatbot will respond with the total number of employees registered in the system.\n\nNote: The chatbot may ask follow-up questions to clarify your query or provide additional information. Please respond accordingly to get the desired result.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:07:28','2026-04-30 19:07:28'),(13,1,'1777576067.052454','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, you can use the chatbot feature. Here\'s a step-by-step guide:\n\n1. **Go to the website**: Open the Municipal Government of Pagsanjan, Laguna website.\n2. **Click on the chat icon**: Look for the chat icon on the website, usually found at the bottom right corner of the page.\n3. **Type your question**: In the chat window, type your question in Filipino: \"ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?\"\n4. **Send the message**: Click the send button or press enter to send your question to the chatbot.\n5. **Wait for the response**: The chatbot will process your question and provide a response. If your question is valid, the chatbot will provide the total number of registered employees in the system.\n6. **View the response**: The chatbot will display the response in the chat window, which should include the total number of registered employees.\n\nNote: The chatbot uses query expansion synonyms, which means it can understand similar phrases or words related to your question. For example, you can also ask \"How many employees are registered in the system?\" or \"What is the total number of employees in the system?\" and the chatbot should still provide the correct response.\n\n**Validation rules**: Please note that the chatbot has validation rules in place to ensure that the question is valid and relevant to the system. If your question is not valid, the chatbot will provide a follow-up question or a message indicating that it cannot understand your question.\n\n**Admin steps**: If you are an admin user, you may have additional options to view the total number of registered employees in the system. To do this:\n\n1. **Log in to the admin dashboard**: Go to the admin login page and enter your credentials.\n2. **Navigate to the employee management page**: Look for the employee management page or section in the admin dashboard.\n3. **View the employee list**: The employee list should display the total number of registered employees in the system.\n\nPlease note that admin access is restricted to authorized personnel only.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:07:49','2026-04-30 19:07:49'),(14,1,'1777576071.142447','How many employees are registered in the system?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, follow these steps:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Log in to the system**: Go to the login page and enter your admin credentials (email and password). Click the \"Login\" button to access the dashboard.\n2. **Navigate to the Personnel page**: Once logged in, click on the \"Personnel\" link in the navigation menu. This will take you to the admin personnel page.\n3. **View the Total Personnel stat**: On the personnel page, look for the \"Total Personnel\" stat card. This card displays the total number of employees registered in the system.\n4. **Check the stat value**: The stat value will display the total number of employees. This is the answer to your question.\n\nAlternatively, if you want to view more detailed information about the employees:\n\n1. **Click on the stat card**: Click on the \"Total Personnel\" stat card to view more detailed information about the employees.\n2. **View the employee list**: This will take you to a page that lists all the employees registered in the system. You can scroll through the list to see the total number of employees.\n\nThat\'s it! By following these steps, you should be able to find out how many employees are registered in the system.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:07:52','2026-04-30 19:07:52'),(15,1,'1777576074.423742','How many employees are there?','There are 11 employees in total, according to our database. I\'ve just run a quick query to get the latest count, and it looks like our team is made up of 11 individuals. If you need more information about our employees, such as their roles or departments, I\'d be happy to help with that as well. Let me know how I can assist you further.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 19:07:55','2026-04-30 19:07:55'),(16,1,'1777576109.956546','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','Kumusta. Ayon sa aming mga record, may 11 na empleyado na nakarehistro sa sistema. Ito ay batay sa resulta ng pagtatanong sa database namin. Kaya, may kabuuang 11 na mga empleyado na nakalista sa ating sistema.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 19:08:32','2026-04-30 19:08:32'),(17,1,'1777576114.208199','How many employees are registered in the system?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:08:34','2026-04-30 19:08:34'),(18,1,'1777576116.712889','How many employees are there?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:08:37','2026-04-30 19:08:37'),(19,1,'1777576147.046105','How many employees are there?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:09:07','2026-04-30 19:09:07'),(20,NULL,'1777576320.244587','ilan ang employees natin?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:12:02','2026-04-30 19:12:02'),(21,1,'1777626981.889425','Paano mag-register ng bagong user','Upang mag-register ng bagong user, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n**Hakbang 1: Pumunta sa Employee Registration Wizard**\nKlik sa button na \"Employee Registration Wizard\" sa dashboard ng admin. Ito ay magbubukas ng isang modal window na may pamagat na \"Employee Registration Wizard\".\n\n**Hakbang 2: Kumpletuhin ang Personal Details**\nSa unang step, ikompleto ang mga personal detail ng bagong user, tulad ng pangalan, apelyido, at iba pang impormasyon. Siguraduhin na lahat ng mga kinakailangang field ay nakumpleto.\n\n**Hakbang 3: Kumpletuhin ang Account Details**\nSa susunod na step, ikompleto ang mga account detail ng bagong user, tulad ng username at password. Siguraduhin na ang password ay malakas at sumusunod sa mga validation rule.\n\n**Hakbang 4: Kumpletuhin ang Employment Details**\nSa susunod na step, ikompleto ang mga employment detail ng bagong user, tulad ng posisyon at departamento. Siguraduhin na lahat ng mga kinakailangang field ay nakumpleto.\n\n**Hakbang 5: Kumpletuhin ang Contact Details**\nSa susunod na step, ikompleto ang mga contact detail ng bagong user, tulad ng email at telepono. Siguraduhin na lahat ng mga kinakailangang field ay nakumpleto.\n\n**Hakbang 6: Kumpletuhin ang Gov IDs**\nSa huling step, ikompleto ang mga Gov IDs ng bagong user, tulad ng TIN at SSS. Siguraduhin na lahat ng mga kinakailangang field ay nakumpleto.\n\n**Hakbang 7: I-save ang Registration**\nPagkatapos kumpletuhin ang lahat ng mga step, klik sa button na \"Save\" upang i-save ang registration. Ang sistemang ay magve-verify sa lahat ng mga impormasyon at mag-create ng bagong account para sa user.\n\n**Admin steps:**\nAng admin ay dapat na mag-verify sa lahat ng mga impormasyon at mag-apruba sa','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\test-chatbot.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\"]','2026-05-01 09:16:25','2026-05-01 09:16:25'),(22,1,'1777627170.409022','ilan ang bilang ng mga total employ dito sa ating system','Mayroon kang 11 na total employ sa ating system. Ito ay ayon sa resulta ng ating query, kung saan nakita natin na may 11 na mga empleyado na nakarehistro. Kaya, ang bilang ng mga total employ dito ay 11.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:19:32','2026-05-01 09:19:32'),(23,1,'1777627181.851425','sino-sino ang lahat ng 11 na employed na students','Database error: 1054 (42S22): Unknown column \'employment_status\' in \'where clause\'','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-01 09:19:44','2026-05-01 09:19:44'),(24,1,'1777627191.184481','inumerate mo lahat ng mga pangalan ng mga employees sa system na \'to','May 11 na mga empleyado sa system natin. Sila ay sina System Administrator, Jeremy Reyes Pogi, Juan Reyes Dela Cruz, Ana Garcia Ramos, Pedro Mendoza Santos Jr., Rosa Flores Bautista, Carlos Torres Gonzales, Luz Aquino Villanueva, Miguel Castro Rivera, at Elena Morales Fernandez. Pwedeng makita ang kanilang buong pangalan sa listahan ng mga empleyado.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:19:52','2026-05-01 09:19:52'),(25,1,'1777627383.380104','enumerate mo lahat ng mga employ natin dito yung mga 11','<p>May 11 na empleyado sa sistema.</p><ul><li>System Admin (EMP-2025-0001)</li><li>Jeremy Reyes Pogi (2024001)</li><li>Juan Reyes Dela Cruz (2024002)</li><li>Ana Garcia Ramos (2024003)</li><li>Pedro Mendoza Santos (2024004)</li><li>Rosa Flores Bautista (2024005)</li><li>Carlos Torres Gonzales (2024006)</li><li>Luz Aquino Villanueva (2024007)</li><li>Miguel Castro Rivera (2024008)</li><li>Elena Morales Fernandez (2024009)</li><li>Roberto Diaz Mercado (2024010)</li></ul>','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:23:05','2026-05-01 09:23:05'),(26,1,'1777627398.131008','Ano ang trabaho ni jeremy pogi dito sa system natin','<p><strong>Maghahanap ng Trabaho ng Isang Empleyado</strong></p><ol><li>Pindutin ang <strong>Chatbot</strong> button sa kanan ng screen.</li><li>Mag-type ng \"Ano ang trabaho ni Jeremy Pogi\" sa chatbox.</li><li>Pindutin ang <strong>Enter</strong> key o pindutin ang <strong>Send</strong> button.</li></ol><ul><li>Opwisyon:</li><li>Mag-type ng \"Find employee Jeremy Pogi\" kung gusto mong mag-English.</li><li>Mag-type ng \"Hanapin ang trabaho ni Jeremy Pogi\" kung gusto mong mag-Filipino.</li></ul><ol><li>Ang chatbot ay magrerespond sa iyong tanong at magpapakita ng trabaho ni Jeremy Pogi.</li></ol><p><strong>Kung Hindi Makita ang Chatbot</strong></p><ol><li>Puntahan ang <strong>Admin</strong> page.</li><li>Hanapin ang <strong>Chatbot</strong> section.</li><li>Pindutin ang <strong>Toggle Chatbot</strong> button.</li></ol><ul><li>Kung wala pa ring chatbot, pindutin ang <strong>HRIS Assistant</strong> button sa itaas ng screen.</li></ul><p><strong>Kung Hindi Nakarehistro si Jeremy Pogi</strong></p><ol><li>Puntahan ang <strong>Employee Registration Wizard</strong> page.</li><li>Punan ang mga kinakailangang impormasyon ni Jeremy Pogi.</li><li>Pindutin ang <strong>Register</strong> button.</li></ol><ul><li>Tandaan: Ang pagrehistro ng empleyado ay dapat gawin ng isang authorized personnel lamang.</li></ul>','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\user\\\\signup.blade.php\"]','2026-05-01 09:23:19','2026-05-01 09:23:19'),(27,1,'1777627424.755463','Ano ang trabaho ni jeremy pogi','Kumusta. Base sa aming database, si Jeremy Pogi ay isang Municipal Mayor. Ito ay nakalagay sa aming employment records, kung saan nakarehistro siya bilang isang Municipal Mayor. Mayroon lamang isang record na nakita kaugnay sa kanyang pangalan at trabaho.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:23:47','2026-05-01 09:23:47'),(28,1,'1777627435.385643','magkano ang sahod ni jeremy pogi sa buwan na \'to','Kumusta? Ang sahod ni Jeremy Pogi sa buwan na ito ay PHP 121,264.00. Ayon sa aming record, ito ang kanyang buwanang rate. Sana ito ay makatulong sa iyo.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:23:57','2026-05-01 09:23:57'),(29,1,'1777627448.711587','ibigay mo ang specific date na unang pumasok si Jeremy pogi at ano ang time in ang timeout niya sa umaga at hapon','Kamusta. Ayon sa aming record, si Jeremy ay unang pumasok noong Pebrero 2, 2026. Sa umaga niyang iyon, pumasok siya ng 7:08 ng umaga at walang record ng timeout. Sa hapon, wala rin siyang time-in pero mayroong time-out na 5:48 ng hapon.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:24:11','2026-05-01 09:24:11'),(30,1,'1777627466.088489','Hanapin mo nga ang lahat ng petsa na kung saan ay na-late ng time in si Jeremy pogi na Pumasok siya ng 801','Kumusta? Sorry to say, pero wala kaming nahanap na petsa na kung saan si Jeremy ay na-late ng time in at pumasok ng 8:01 ng umaga. Ang aming query ay hindi nakahanap ng anumang record na sumusunod sa mga kondisyong iyon. Ibig sabihin, walang PHP 0.00 na halaga o anumang impormasyon na nakolekta tungkol sa mga late na pagpasok ni Jeremy. Kung may ibang tanong ka, feel free to ask!','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:24:28','2026-05-01 09:24:28'),(31,1,'1777627478.613135','ano ang mga date na kung saan pumasok si Jeremy pogi ng late','To find out the dates when Jeremy Pogi was late, follow these steps:\n\n**Step 1: Log in to the system**\nGo to the login page and enter your credentials (email and password). Click the \"Login\" button to proceed.\n\n**Step 2: Navigate to the Attendance page**\nAfter logging in, click on the \"Attendance\" tab or button to access the attendance page.\n\n**Step 3: Select the employee**\nOn the attendance page, select \"Jeremy Pogi\" from the list of employees or use the search function to find him.\n\n**Step 4: Choose the date range**\nSelect the start and end dates for which you want to view Jeremy Pogi\'s attendance records. You can choose a specific month or a custom date range.\n\n**Step 5: Filter by attendance status**\nLook for a filter or dropdown menu that allows you to select the attendance status. Choose \"Late\" to view only the dates when Jeremy Pogi was late.\n\n**Step 6: View the attendance records**\nAfter applying the filters, you should see a list of dates when Jeremy Pogi was late. You can scroll through the list to view the specific dates.\n\n**Step 7: Use the chatbot (optional)**\nIf you prefer to use the chatbot, you can type a message like \"What are the dates when Jeremy Pogi was late?\" The chatbot will respond with the relevant information.\n\nNote: The exact steps may vary depending on the system\'s user interface and functionality. If you\'re having trouble finding the attendance records or using the chatbot, you can contact the system administrator for assistance.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\"]','2026-05-01 09:24:40','2026-05-01 09:24:40'),(32,1,'1777627767.417867','Paano natin malalaman kung late ang isang employees system natin','Upang malaman kung late ang isang employee sa inyong system, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n**Hakbang 1: Puntahan ang Attendance Page**\nPuntahan ang page para sa attendance ng mga empleyado. Ito ay makikita sa admin panel ng inyong system.\n\n**Hakbang 2: Piliin ang Employee**\nPiliin ang employee na nais ninyong malaman kung late sila. Makikita ito sa listahan ng mga empleyado.\n\n**Hakbang 3: Tingnan ang Attendance Record**\nTingnan ang attendance record ng employee na pinili ninyo. Ito ay makikita sa isang table o listahan na nagpapakita ng mga sumusunod na impormasyon:\n- Date\n- Time-in\n- Time-out\n- Status (present, late, absent, etc.)\n\n**Hakbang 4: Tingnan ang Time-in**\nTingnan ang time-in ng employee sa araw na nais ninyong malaman kung late sila. Kung ang time-in ay higit sa 8:15 AM (o anumang oras na itinakda ng inyong kumpanya), ibig sabihin ay late ang employee.\n\n**Hakbang 5: Tingnan ang Status**\nTingnan ang status ng employee sa araw na iyon. Kung ang status ay \"late\", ibig sabihin ay late ang employee.\n\nKung nais ninyong malaman ang mga detalye tungkol sa attendance ng isang employee, maaari ninyong puntahan ang attendance page at piliin ang employee na nais ninyong malaman.\n\n**Admin Steps:**\nKung kayo ay admin, maaari ninyong mag-login sa inyong account at puntahan ang admin panel upang malaman ang attendance ng mga empleyado. Maaari ninyong piliin ang employee na nais ninyong malaman at tingnan ang kanilang attendance record.\n\nPaalala: Ang mga hakbang sa itaas ay base sa mga impormasyon na nakikita sa mga codebase file na binigay. Maaaring magkakaiba ang mga hakbang depende sa mga partikular na kinakail','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\test-chatbot.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\"]','2026-05-01 09:29:30','2026-05-01 09:29:30'),(33,1,'1777627884.349336','pwede mo bang hanapin lahat ng mga pangalan at date kung sino sino \'yung mga employ na late','Kumusta. Mayroon tayong 2 na record ng mga empleyado na late. Si Jeremy Reyes Pogi ang nakalista na late noong April 1 at 2, 2026. Ito ang mga tala ng mga empleyado na dumating ng mahina sa oras.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:31:26','2026-05-01 09:31:26'),(34,1,'1777627916.624405','Pwede mo bang ibigay lahat ng mga details na alam mo kay Jeremy pogi','Database error: 1054 (42S22): Unknown column \'description\' in \'where clause\'','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-01 09:31:58','2026-05-01 09:31:58'),(35,1,'1777627928.957938','Pwede mo bang ibigay lahat ng details na alam mo kay Jeremy pogi','Hi there, sorry to inform you that I couldn\'t find any information on a person named Jeremy Handsome in our database. It\'s possible that the details are not in our system or the name is incorrect. I\'ve checked thoroughly, but unfortunately, no records were found. If you have any more questions or need help with something else, feel free to ask.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:32:10','2026-05-01 09:32:10'),(36,1,'1777627945.575928','Sino ba si Jeremy pogi','Kamusta. We found one employee named Jeremy Pogi in our database. His full name is Jeremy Reyes Pogi. If you need more information about him, feel free to ask.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:32:27','2026-05-01 09:32:27'),(37,1,'1777627956.70482','pwede mo bang hanapin lahat ng details kay Jeremy pogi sa system natin','I found Jeremy Pogi\'s details in our system. Jeremy is a permanent employee with the title of Municipal Mayor, and his monthly rate is PHP 121,264.00. He was appointed on January 15, 2024, and his contact number is 09175983896. If you need more information, feel free to ask!','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:32:39','2026-05-01 09:32:39'),(38,1,'1777627975.793863','Paano malalaman yung bilang ng employee or total ng bilang na employ sa system natin','Mayroon kang 11 na empleyado sa ating sistema, ayon sa resulta ng ating query. Ito ang kabuuang bilang ng mga empleyado na nakarehistro sa ating database. Kaya, kung gusto mong malaman ang bilang ng mga empleyado, ito na ang sagot - 11.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:32:57','2026-05-01 09:32:57'),(39,1,'1777627993.925108','Paano mag-update ng details ng isang employee natin mali yung pangalan ni jeremy pogi Gusto ko siyang baguhin sa Jeremy ganda','Upang mag-update ng details ng isang employee, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n1. **Punta sa Admin Panel**: Una, puntahan ang admin panel ng system. Ito ay naroroon sa itaas na parte ng webpage.\n2. **Piliin ang \"Personnel\"**: Sa admin panel, piliin ang \"Personnel\" o \"Mga Kawani\" na tab. Ito ay magpapakita ng listahan ng lahat ng mga empleyado.\n3. **Hanapin si Jeremy Pogi**: Sa listahan ng mga empleyado, hanapin si Jeremy Pogi. Pwede mong gamitin ang search bar upang hanapin siya.\n4. **Pindutin ang \"Edit\" Button**: Kapag nakita mo si Jeremy Pogi, pindutin ang \"Edit\" button na nasa tabi ng kanyang pangalan. Ito ay magpapakita ng isang bagong window kung saan pwede mong i-edit ang kanyang details.\n5. **I-edit ang Pangalan**: Sa bagong window, hanapin ang \"Pangalan\" o \"Name\" field at i-edit ito mula sa \"Jeremy Pogi\" patungo sa \"Jeremy Ganda\".\n6. **Pindutin ang \"Save\" Button**: Kapag tapos ka na sa pag-e-edit, pindutin ang \"Save\" button upang i-save ang mga pagbabago.\n7. **Tiningnan ang Pagbabago**: Matapos i-save ang mga pagbabago, tiningnan ang listahan ng mga empleyado upang siguraduhin na ang pangalan ni Jeremy ay nagbabago na sa \"Jeremy Ganda\".\n\nGanito ang mga hakbang upang mag-update ng details ng isang employee. Siguraduhin na susundin ang lahat ng mga hakbang upang makapag-edit ng details ng isang employee nang maayos.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\"]','2026-05-01 09:33:16','2026-05-01 09:33:16'),(40,1,'1777628735.278824','hahah','I couldn\'t find relevant information in the codebase about this topic. Could you rephrase your question?','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:45:35','2026-05-01 09:45:35'),(41,1,'1777628828.992727','Sino si Anna Ramos','Kamusta? I tried to look up information on Anna Ramos, pero sadly, wala kaming nakuhang record about her. It seems she\'s not in our database of employees. If you have more details or context about Anna Ramos, I\'d be happy to try and help you further. Anyway, let me know if there\'s anything else I can assist you with.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:47:11','2026-05-01 09:47:11'),(42,1,'1777629186.62312','Who works in Mayor office?','We\'ve found the list of employees working in the Mayor\'s Office. There are 7 employees in total, and they are Jeremy Reyes Pogi, Juan Reyes Dela Cruz, Ana Garcia Ramos, Pedro Mendoza Santos, Rosa Flores Bautista, Carlos Torres Gonzales, and Luz Aquino Villanueva. If you need more information about these employees, such as their job titles or contact details, feel free to ask and we can try to assist you further.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-01 09:53:09','2026-05-01 09:53:09'),(43,NULL,'1777709389.565116','paano mag file ng leave?','Upang mag-file ng leave, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n**Hakbang 1: Pumunta sa Website ng Munisipalidad**\nBuksan ang browser at pumunta sa website ng Munisipalidad ng Pagsanjan, Laguna.\n\n**Hakbang 2: Pumunta sa Services Section**\nSa website, pumunta sa section na \"Services\" at hanapin ang link na \"Leave Application\" o \"File a Leave\".\n\n**Hakbang 3: Punta sa Leave Application Form**\nKapag nakapunta na sa Leave Application Form, punta sa section na \"File a Leave\" at pindutin ang button na \"Apply for Leave\".\n\n**Hakbang 4: Punta sa Login Page (kung kinakailangan)**\nKung hindi ka pa nakalog-in, punta sa login page at log-in ka gamit ang iyong username at password.\n\n**Hakbang 5: Pumunta sa Leave Application Form**\nKapag nakalog-in na, punta sa Leave Application Form at punta sa section na \"File a Leave\".\n\n**Hakbang 6: Pumuno ng Leave Application Form**\nPumuno ng Leave Application Form ng mga sumusunod na detalye:\n * Tipo ng leave (e.g. sick leave, vacation leave, etc.)\n * Petsa ng leave\n * Rason ng leave\n * Ibang mga detalye na kinakailangan\n\n**Hakbang 7: I-upload ang mga Kinakailangang Dokumento (kung kinakailangan)**\nKung kinakailangan, i-upload ang mga dokumento na kinakailangan para sa leave application, tulad ng mga resibo ng pagpapagamot o iba pang mga dokumento.\n\n**Hakbang 8: I-sumite ang Leave Application**\nKapag kumpleto na ang lahat ng detalye, pindutin ang button na \"Submit\" para i-sumite ang leave application.\n\n**Hakbang 9: Maghintay ng Approval**\nMaghintay ng approval ng leave application. Ang approval ay maaaring matanggap sa pamamagitan ng email o iba pang paraan.\n\n**Mahalagang Paalala:**\nSiguraduhin na sundin ang mga p','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\test-chatbot.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\"]','2026-05-02 08:09:52','2026-05-02 08:09:52'),(44,NULL,'1778112239.644163','magkano ang hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi/','Database error: 1054 (42S22): Unknown column \'T2.hourly_rate\' in \'field list\'','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-07 00:04:01','2026-05-07 00:04:01'),(45,NULL,'1778112271.591131','paano na nacompute ang hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi?','Upang ma-compute ang hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n**Hakbang 1: Pumunta sa Employee Registration Wizard**\n- Pumunta sa website ng Municipal Government ng Pagsanjan, Laguna at mag-login bilang Admin.\n- Piliin ang \"Employee Registration Wizard\" sa mga opsyon.\n\n**Hakbang 2: Piliin ang Employee**\n- Sa \"Employee Registration Wizard\", piliin ang \"Search\" o \"Find\" tab upang hanapin si Jeremy Pogi.\n- I-type ang pangalan ni Jeremy Pogi sa search bar at pindutin ang \"Search\" button.\n- Kung si Jeremy Pogi ay matatagpuan, piliin ang kanyang pangalan sa resulta ng search.\n\n**Hakbang 3: Pumunta sa Employment Details**\n- Sa \"Employee Registration Wizard\", pumunta sa \"Employment\" tab.\n- Sa \"Employment\" tab, hanapin ang \"Hourly Rate\" o \"Salary\" section.\n- Kung wala ito, pumunta sa \"Add New Employment\" o \"Edit Employment\" button upang maidagdag o ma-update ang impormasyon tungkol sa employment ni Jeremy Pogi.\n\n**Hakbang 4: Compute ang Hourly Rate**\n- Sa \"Employment\" tab, hanapin ang \"Hourly Rate\" o \"Salary\" field.\n- Kung mayroong \"Compute Hourly Rate\" button, pindutin ito upang ma-compute ang hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi.\n- Kung wala, kailangan mong manual na mag-compute ng hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi batay sa kanyang annual salary at working hours.\n\n**Hakbang 5: I-save ang Changes**\n- Matapos ma-compute ang hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi, pindutin ang \"Save\" o \"Update\" button upang i-save ang changes.\n\n**Hakbang 6: Tignan ang Resulta**\n- Matapos i-save ang changes, pumunta sa \"Employee Registration Wizard\" at piliin ang \"View\" o \"Details\" tab upang tignan ang updated na hourly rate ni Jeremy Pogi.\n\nKung mayroong problema o katanungan, pumunta sa \"Help\" o \"Support\" section','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"routes\\\\web.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\"]','2026-05-07 00:04:34','2026-05-07 00:04:34'),(46,NULL,'1778114347.448117','saan galing yang 10, 335  na basic pay ni jeremy pogi?','Hi, I\'ve checked the database for Jeremy Pogi\'s salary computation with a basic pay of PHP 10,335.00, but unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any records matching that amount. It\'s possible that the data isn\'t available or the basic pay might be incorrect. If you\'d like to try again or check a different amount, feel free to ask and I\'ll be happy to help.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:39:09','2026-05-07 00:39:09'),(47,NULL,'1778114376.193438','bakit merong deduction sa salary si Jeremy Pogi?','Hi, I\'ve checked on Jeremy Pogi\'s salary computation, but unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any records. It\'s possible that his data hasn\'t been updated or is not available in our system. If you need more information, I can try to help you look into it further. For now, I don\'t have any details on any deductions from his salary, as there are no records found.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:39:37','2026-05-07 00:39:37'),(48,NULL,'1778114396.278568','Magkano ang deduction sa Late ni Jeremy Pogi?','Kumusta? Based sa result ng query, wala pong recorded deduction sa late ni Jeremy Pogi. Ibig sabihin, hindi pa siya nakakaranas ng late deduction o wala pang naitalang deduction sa kanyang salary computation. Kaya, ang deduction sa late niya ay walang halaga, o PHP 0.00.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:39:58','2026-05-07 00:39:58'),(49,NULL,'1778114589.110927','saan galing yung late deduction ni Jeremy pogi?','Hi, I\'ve checked on Jeremy\'s late deduction for you. Unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any information on it in our database. It seems that there are no records of a late deduction for Jeremy, so I don\'t have an amount to share with you. If you need more help or have any other questions, feel free to ask.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:43:10','2026-05-07 00:43:10'),(50,NULL,'1778114669.127247','saan galing yung late deduction ni Jeremy pogi?','Hi there, I found some info about Jeremy\'s late deduction. It looks like he had one instance where he was late, resulting in a deduction of PHP 689.00, which is equivalent to 60 minutes of late arrival. The other two records show no late deductions, so it seems this was an isolated incident. The deduction comes from his attendance record, where his late arrival time was logged and computed as a deduction based on his hourly rate.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:44:31','2026-05-07 00:44:31'),(51,NULL,'1778114767.537758','paano na compute ang 14, 469 na basic pay ni jeremy pogi?','Upang makompyut ang 14,469 na basic pay ni Jeremy Pogi, sumusunod ang mga hakbang:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Pumunta sa Employee Registration Wizard**: Punta sa modal ng Employee Registration Wizard sa pamamagitan ng pag-click sa isang button o link na nakalagay sa dashboard ng admin.\n2. **Piliin ang Employee**: Piliin ang pangalan ni Jeremy Pogi mula sa listahan ng mga empleyado.\n3. **Punta sa Step 3: Employment**: Pindot sa \"Next\" hanggang sa makarating sa Step 3: Employment.\n4. **Ilagay ang Basic Pay**: Sa ilalim ng \"Employment Details\", ilagay ang 14,469 sa field na \"Basic Pay\".\n5. **Pindot sa \"Next\"**: Pindot sa \"Next\" upang iproseso ang impormasyon.\n\n**Hindi na kailangang gawin ng admin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang**:\n\n* **Automatic Computation**: Ang sistema ay awtomatikong magkakompyut ng mga benepisyo at iba pang mga detalye na may kaugnayan sa basic pay ni Jeremy Pogi.\n* **I-save ang Impormasyon**: Ang sistema ay i-save ang impormasyon ni Jeremy Pogi, kasama ang kanyang basic pay.\n\n**Kung hindi mo alam kung paano pumunta sa Employee Registration Wizard**, mangyaring humingi ng tulong sa iyong supervisor o administrator.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"routes\\\\web.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-05-07 00:46:09','2026-05-07 00:46:09'),(52,NULL,'1778114831.759014','why does there is 1378 undertime deduction of jeremy pogi?','I\'ve checked the records for Jeremy Pogi, but unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any information that matches an undertime deduction of 1,378 Philippine Pesos. It\'s possible that this specific deduction doesn\'t exist or wasn\'t recorded in our system. If you\'re looking for details on undertime deductions, they\'re usually calculated based on attendance records, specifically when an employee leaves early, and the amount is computed as a fraction of their hourly rate. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:47:13','2026-05-07 00:47:13'),(53,NULL,'1778114974.04115','why does there is 1378 undertime deduction of jeremy pogi?','I\'ve checked the records for Jeremy Pogi, but unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any results that match the undertime deduction of 1,378 Philippine Pesos. It\'s possible that the deduction was calculated based on attendance records, where undertime minutes are converted to a deduction amount using the hourly rate. If you\'d like to investigate further, we can try to find the underlying attendance records that may have caused this deduction.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:49:36','2026-05-07 00:49:36'),(54,NULL,'1778114997.457465','what is that 12, 402.00  of jeremy pogi?','I\'ve checked the records for Jeremy Pogi, and unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any information matching the daily gross pay of PHP 12,402.00. It\'s possible that the amount is incorrect or Jeremy Pogi doesn\'t have a record with that specific daily gross pay. If you have any more questions or need help with something else, feel free to ask.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-05-07 00:49:59','2026-05-07 00:49:59');
